00:12:19,523 --> 00:12:20,980
YOU MEAN THIS?

251
00:12:20,980 --> 00:12:23,529
HEY, HURRY,
AND DO SOMETHING.

252
00:12:25,522 --> 00:12:26,525
DAMN.

