YOUR OWN STRENGTH.

275
00:13:26,112 --> 00:13:27,280
HAH!

276
00:13:28,528 --> 00:13:30,528
[yells]

277
00:13:30,528 --> 00:13:31,951
Ibara:
FIRE TO OUR SIX!

278
00:13:31,951 --> 00:13:32,986
Gennai: YOU GOT IT!

279
00:13:39,528 --> 00:13:41,261
AH, HELL, YEAH.

