IT A LITTLE?

283
00:13:47,525 --> 00:13:48,527
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

284
00:13:48,527 --> 00:13:50,103
THE FLAMES LAST
ONLY AN INSTANT,

285
00:13:50,103 --> 00:13:52,138
BUT THE OZU SISTERS
ARE DEFINITELY

286
00:13:52,138 --> 00:13:54,107
GOING TO BE KNOCKED OUT
FOR A WHILE.

287
00:13:54,107 --> 00:13:55,522
[all gasp]

288
00:13:55,522 --> 00:13:57,010
Kurobe: HOLY CRAP.

289
00:13:57,010 --> 00:14:00,522
