PISSED ME OFF.

293
00:14:05,118 --> 00:14:07,887
SO WHAT'S
HER SPECIAL ABILITY?

294
00:14:07,887 --> 00:14:10,522
UM, I REALLY
DON'T KNOW.

295
00:14:10,522 --> 00:14:11,858
[crackling]
HEH!

296
00:14:18,530 --> 00:14:19,899
[grunts]

297
00:14:19,899 --> 00:14:21,167
[thunder crashes]

298
00:14:22,902 --> 00:14:24,522
OH, MY GOD.

299
00:14:24,522 --> 00:14:26,528
W-WHAT WAS THAT?

300
00:14:26,528 --> 00:14:29,242
IS THAT
HER SPECIAL ABILITY,

301
00:14:29,242 --> 00:14:30,528
SHOOTING
ELECTRICITY?

302
00:14:32,522 --> 00:14:34,080
I'M TOLD THEY WOVE

303
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:37,217
ELECTRIC EEL
SEQUENCES
INTO MY DNA.

304
00:14:37,217 --> 00:14:40,286
WHAT THE HELL WAS
OUR BELOVED SCHOOL
THINKING?

305
00:14:41,921 --> 00:14:43,526
THEY SHOULD HAVE
THOUGHT TWICE

306
00:14:43,526 --> 00:14:45,892
ABOUT MESSING WITH
MY BODY LIKE THIS.

307
00:14:45,892 --> 00:14:47,894
IN ORDER TO GET
THE RESCUE TEAMS

308
00:14:47,894 --> 00:14:49,829
TO THE SITE
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE,

309
00:14:49,829 --> 00:14:52,232
THEY HAD NO CHOICE
BUT TO PUSH THE BOUNDARIES

310
00:14:52,232 --> 00:14:53,531
AND TIMING
OF THEIR RESEARCH.

311
00:14:53,531 --> 00:14:56,035
THERE GOAL WAS
TO SAVE LIVES.

312
00:14:56,035 --> 00:14:58,522
HUMAN EXPERIMENT WAS
NEVER THEIR INTENT.

313
00:15:00,106 --> 00:15:02,108
[thunder crashes]
[gasping]

314
00:15:06,112 --> 00:15:09,522
YOU KNOW WHAT,
CLASS PRESIDENT
IBARA NARUSE?

315
00:15:09,522 --> 00:15:12,085
EVERYTHING YOU SAID
JUST SOUNDS LIKE

316
00:15:12,085 --> 00:15:14,531
A LOT OF SILLY
WISHFUL THINKING TO ME.

317
00:15:14,531 --> 00:15:16,856
ADMIT IT.
YOU'RE WORRIED

318
00:15:16,856 --> 00:15:18,858
OUT OF YOUR MIND,
AREN'T YOU?

319
00:15:18,858 --> 00:15:21,895
WE'RE NO DIFFERENT THAN
THESE CHEAP, DISPOSABLE
HAND WARMERS.

320
00:15:23,263 --> 00:15:25,164
WE'RE MANUFACTURED
AND USED UP

321
00:15:25,164 --> 00:15:26,526
WITHOUT
A SECOND THOUGHT,

322
00:15:26,526 --> 00:15:28,835
AND THEN WHEN WE'RE
OF NO USE ANYMORE...

323
00:15:31,523 --> 00:15:33,973
Haruto:
SO HOW LONG
WILL WE LIVE?

324
00:15:33,973 --> 00:15:34,974
HUH?

325
00:15:34,974 --> 00:15:36,276
Mishima:
WE'RE NOT SURE.

326
00:15:36,276 --> 00:15:38,523
NOW IT'S ALL STARTING
TO MAKE SOME SENSE,

327
00:15:38,523 --> 00:15:40,526
THE REASON WHY
YOU AND YOUR SCIENTISTS

328
00:15:40,526 --> 00:15:42,882
DECIDED TO GIVE US
THE NAME COPPELION.

329
00:15:42,882 --> 00:15:44,530
IT'S SO THAT
WHEN WE DIE OFF,

330
00:15:44,530 --> 00:15:47,530
NONE OF YOU
WILL HAVE TO FEEL
ANY REMORSE OR GUILT.

331
00:15:47,530 --> 00:15:50,056
AT SOME POINT,
WE'LL JUST DROP DEAD

332
00:15:50,056 --> 00:15:52,258
LIKE A LAB RAT
DURING A TEST.

333
00:15:52,258 --> 00:15:56,527
Kanon: DO YOU UNDERSTAND
WHAT THAT MEANS,
IBARA NARUSE?

334
00:15:56,527 --> 00:15:58,965
WE COPPELION ARE ALL
CONDEMNED TO DIE

335
00:15:58,965 --> 00:16:00,529
SUDDENLY AND
WITHOUT ANY WARNING.

336
00:16:02,168 --> 00:16:04,527
IT'LL JUST HAPPEN
ONE DAY.

337
00:16:04,527 --> 00:16:07,273
THE WARMTH
IN OUR BODIES
WILL LEAVE US.

338
00:16:07,273 --> 00:16:10,176
IT COULD BE
NEXT YEAR,
NEXT WEEK,

339
00:16:10,176 --> 00:16:12,530
OR IT COULD EVEN
HAPPEN TONIGHT,

340
00:16:12,530 --> 00:16:14,527
AND THAT'S IT.
WE'RE DONE.

341
00:16:14,527 --> 00:16:18,117
NO ONE KNOWS
HOW LONG WE'LL
BE ALIVE.

342
00:16:18,117 --> 00:16:19,986
IT CAN'T BE.
HMM?

343
00:16:19,986 --> 00:16:21,524
DID THEY
REALLY SAY THAT,

344
00:16:21,524 --> 00:16:24,123
BOTH HARUTO AND
THE VICE PRINCIPAL?

345
00:16:25,522 --> 00:16:27,193
DO YOU
UNDERSTAND IT NOW?

346
00:16:27,193 --> 00:16:29,896
WE ARE AT WAR
WITH HUMANITY.

347
00:16:29,896 --> 00:16:32,526
EITHER WE'LL BE
THE ONES TO DIE FIRST,

348
00:16:32,526 --> 00:16:36,169
OR WE DESTROY THEM
BEFORE WE LET THAT
HAPPEN.

349
00:16:36,169 --> 00:16:38,524
YOU SHOULD REALLY
CONSIDER JOINING US.

350
00:16:38,524 --> 00:16:40,139
IT WOULD BE SO GREAT.

351
00:16:40,139 --> 00:16:41,525
WITH OUR
COMBINED EFFORTS,

352
00:16:41,525 --> 00:16:43,276
WE'D BE
AN UNSTOPPABLE FORCE.

353
00:16:43,276 --> 00:16:46,245
WE CAN KILL
THE VICE PRINCIPAL
TOGETHER.

354
00:16:46,245 --> 00:16:47,528
WHAT DO YOU SAY?

355
00:16:47,528 --> 00:16:49,182
I REFUSE!

356
00:16:49,182 --> 00:16:51,150
WHAT?

357
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:52,251
IT'S THEIR FAULT.

358
00:16:52,251 --> 00:16:54,120
HOW CAN YOU?

359
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:57,530
IT'S THE HUMANS
WHO ARE RESPONSIBLE
FOR OUR PITIFUL FATE.

360
00:16:57,530 --> 00:17:00,026
[sighs]
IT'S INEVITABLE.

361
00:17:01,127 --> 00:17:03,096
ALL LIVING THINGS
WILL DIE.

362
00:17:03,096 --> 00:17:05,522
THERE'S NOTHING
WE CAN DO ABOUT IT.

363
00:17:09,268 --> 00:17:11,270
GOD, YOU'RE AN IDIOT.

364
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:14,524
IT'S NOT LIKE DEATH
WILL GREET US PEACEFULLY

365
00:17:14,524 --> 00:17:16,522
WHILE WE'RE LYING
IN OUR BEDS, YOU KNOW.

366
00:17:16,522 --> 00:17:18,144
GET REAL!

367
00:17:18,144 --> 00:17:20,279
THAT MORNING OF OUR
SEND-OFF CEREMONY,

368
00:17:20,279 --> 00:17:23,116
I DON'T KNOW WHY,
BUT I HAD A FEELING

369
00:17:23,116 --> 00:17:24,984
I'D NEVER RETURN
TO OSAKA AGAIN.

370
00:17:24,984 --> 00:17:27,528
MAYBE IT WAS
MY DNA TELLING ME

371
00:17:27,528 --> 00:17:30,056
THAT I DIDN'T
HAVE THAT MUCH TIME
LEFT TO LIVE.

372
00:17:30,056 --> 00:17:31,157
HMM.
OH.

373
00:17:31,157 --> 00:17:33,523
SO IF WHAT YOU SAY
IS TRUE, KANON,

374
00:17:33,523 --> 00:17:36,029
THEN I'LL LIVE MY LIFE
TO THE FULLEST HERE.

375
00:17:36,029 --> 00:17:38,131
THAT WILL BE
GOOD ENOUGH FOR ME.

376
00:17:40,967 --> 00:17:43,970
THAT WOULD
NEVER WORK FOR ME.

377
00:17:43,970 --> 00:17:46,527
LOOK AT THIS FILTHY,
CONTAMINATED CITY,

378
00:17:46,527 --> 00:17:49,275
THIS GODFORSAKEN PLACE
THAT HUMANS FEAR.

379
00:17:49,275 --> 00:17:52,529
I WANT THE WHOLE WORLD
TO END UP LIKE THIS.

380
00:17:52,529 --> 00:17:55,181
UNTIL I
MAKE THAT HAPPEN,

381
00:17:55,181 --> 00:17:57,183
THE ELECTRICITY IN ME

382
00:17:57,183 --> 00:17:59,185
WILL NOT BE STOPPED!

383
00:17:59,185 --> 00:18:01,524
GET OUT OF THERE,
IBARA!

384
00:18:01,524 --> 00:18:02,955
YOU WON'T GET AWAY.

385
00:18:02,955 --> 00:18:03,923
[thunder crashes]
DIE!

386
00:18:08,529 --> 00:18:09,996
[gasps]

387
00:18:09,996 --> 00:18:12,832
IF YOU DECIDE TO BREAK
THE RULES, KANON OZU,

388
00:18:12,832 --> 00:18:15,001
THEN YOU
GET PUNISHED!

389
00:18:17,526 --> 00:18:19,105
WAY TO GO!

390
00:18:19,105 --> 00:18:21,240
YOU TOOK HER DOWN
IN ONE PUNCH.

391
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,942
JUST TO BE SAFE,

392
00:18:22,942 --> 00:18:25,845
I'M GOING
TO SEDATE THEM WITH
MY TRANQUILIZER GUN.

393
00:18:25,845 --> 00:18:28,147
LET'S HOPE
IT WORKS ON THEM.

394
00:18:29,148 --> 00:18:30,950
[sighs]

395
00:18:30,950 --> 00:18:31,951
[dart thwips]

396
00:18:34,053 --> 00:18:35,529
WELL, I COULD
TELL YOU THIS MUCH.

397
00:18:35,529 --> 00:18:37,256
I DON'T WANT
TO TAKE THESE GIRLS

398
00:18:37,256 --> 00:18:38,858
BACK TO THE PLANET
WITH US.

399
00:18:38,858 --> 00:18:41,227
DID YOU SAY
WE'RE GOING BACK
TO THE PLANET?

400
00:18:41,227 --> 00:18:43,029
BUT WE CAME
ALL THIS WAY OUT

401
00:18:43,029 --> 00:18:44,197
TO GET
TO THE HOSPITAL.

402
00:18:44,197 --> 00:18:46,032
AND THESE GIRLS
CHANGED OUR PLAN,

403
00:18:46,032 --> 00:18:47,531
SO WE HAVE
TO GO BACK.

404
00:18:47,531 --> 00:18:48,935
IT WON'T BE
THAT EASY.

405
00:18:48,935 --> 00:18:49,936
HUH?
HUH?

406
00:18:49,936 --> 00:18:51,523
WAIT A SEC.

407
00:18:51,523 --> 00:18:52,530
SO YOU'RE SAYING
THEY SURROUNDED

408
00:18:52,530 --> 00:18:54,941
THE ENTIRE AREA
WITH WASTE?

409
00:18:54,941 --> 00:18:57,523
THE BASTARDS HAVE US
TRAPPED IN HERE?

410
00:18:57,523 --> 00:18:59,912
THE WIND IS
STARTING TO PICK UP.

411
00:19:03,015 --> 00:19:06,529
MISS AOI,
I HAVE BROUGHT YOU
YOUR 3:00 SWEETS.

412
00:19:06,529 --> 00:19:08,955
SWEETS?

413
00:19:08,955 --> 00:19:11,257
NICE TRY THERE.

414
00:19:11,257 --> 00:19:14,127
YOU'RE NOT FOOLING ME
THAT EASY, MR. NO-SENSE.

415
00:19:14,127 --> 00:19:15,527
LEAVE
THE SWEETS THERE.

416
00:19:15,527 --> 00:19:17,522
THEN GET LOST!

417
00:19:21,523 --> 00:19:24,036
WAIT! YOU'RE
REALLY LEAVING?

418
00:19:25,522 --> 00:19:26,522
PLEASE COME BACK.

419
00:19:27,940 --> 00:19:30,977
MISS AOI, WHY DO
YOU KEEP YOURSELF

420
00:19:30,977 --> 00:19:33,146
LOCKED INSIDE
OF THIS STOREROOM?

421
00:19:33,146 --> 00:19:35,524
I, NO-SENSE,
AM A ROBOT.

422
00:19:35,524 --> 00:19:38,528
BUT I POSSESS
DEEP EMOTIONAL
SENSITIVITY.

423
00:19:38,528 --> 00:19:41,087
HOWEVER,
SINCE THE DAY
I WAS CREATED,

424
00:19:41,087 --> 00:19:43,529
