OUTSIDE THE PLANET.

425
00:19:43,529 --> 00:19:45,529
I DO NOT KNOW
WHAT IT MEANS

426
00:19:45,529 --> 00:19:47,927
TO FEEL
THE WARM RAYS
OF THE SUN

427
00:19:47,927 --> 00:19:50,523
OR THE FEELING
OF THE BREEZE
CARESSING MY CHEEK.

428
00:19:50,523 --> 00:19:52,131
BUT YOU'RE
JUST A ROBOT.

429
00:19:52,131 --> 00:19:54,526
EVEN IF A BREEZE
DID BLOW ON YOUR CHEEK,

430
00:19:54,526 --> 00:19:56,135
I DON'T THINK
YOU'D FEEL IT.

431
00:19:56,135 --> 00:19:57,528
THAT IS CORRECT.

432
00:19:57,528 --> 00:19:59,205
I AM A ROBOT.

433
00:19:59,205 --> 00:20:00,907
I AM BUT
AN IMITATION,

434
00:20:00,907 --> 00:20:02,942
A MODEL BASED
ON A HUMAN BEING.

435
00:20:02,942 --> 00:20:06,212
THAT IS WHY I
ENVY YOU, MISS AOI.

436
00:20:06,212 --> 00:20:07,980
YOU POSSESS
FREE WILL

437
00:20:07,980 --> 00:20:11,522
AND CAN GO OUTSIDE
TO FEEL THE BREEZE
AS YOU PLEASE.

438
00:20:11,522 --> 00:20:13,152
YOU'RE BETTER OFF
NOT KNOWING

439
00:20:13,152 --> 00:20:15,154
WHAT IT'S LIKE
ON THE OUTSIDE.

440
00:20:15,154 --> 00:20:19,529
I MEAN, THE BREEZE
IN THIS CITY'S
SO CONTAMINATED.

441
00:20:19,529 --> 00:20:21,528
MISS AOI.

442
00:20:23,129 --> 00:20:25,522
Gennai, over radio:
HEY, NO-SENSE!

443
00:20:25,522 --> 00:20:27,033
IT'S ME, GENNAI!

444
00:20:27,033 --> 00:20:28,835
OPEN THE GATE!

445
00:20:31,938 --> 00:20:33,906
