SPECIFIC SPOTS.

451
00:20:46,185 --> 00:20:48,187
OH, MY GOD!
LOOK AT THIS!

452
00:20:48,187 --> 00:20:49,922
EVERYTHING THAT'S
SHOWING UP HERE

453
00:20:49,922 --> 00:20:51,529
