CRITICAL LEVELS!

454
00:20:51,529 --> 00:20:54,994
Ibara: THE ASTRONOMICAL
OBSERVATORY?

455
00:21:01,526 --> 00:21:05,204
THE SUN DISAPPEARED.

456
00:21:06,524 --> 00:21:07,526
HALT!

457
00:21:07,526 --> 00:21:08,531
PUT YOUR HANDS UP!

458
00:21:08,531 --> 00:21:11,010
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

459
00:21:11,010 --> 00:21:13,529
TAKING
AN AFTERNOON STROLL.

460
00:21:13,529 --> 00:21:16,048
I JUST GOT
TIRED OF WORKING
AT MY DESK.

461
00:21:16,048 --> 00:21:18,524
THIS ONE IS
ALSO A COPPELION.

462
00:21:18,524 --> 00:21:19,526
TAKE HIM IN.

463
00:21:19,526 --> 00:21:21,530
[chirping]
HUH?

464
00:21:21,530 --> 00:21:23,528
HEY, THE BIRD'S
FREAKING OUT.

465
00:21:23,528 --> 00:21:25,526
SHUT UP! CAN'T YOU
SEE I'M BUSY?

466
00:21:25,526 --> 00:21:26,959
