THIS ISN'T RIGHT.

472
00:21:37,525 --> 00:21:41,140
THE WASTE SHOULD BE SOUTH
OF THE ASTRONOMICAL
OBSERVATORY.

473
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:42,530
IT'S THE WIND.

